# API Keys for LLM-powered features (Vibe-Trading, TradingAgents)
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys.
# The backtest and paper trader work WITHOUT any API key.
# You only need these for the LLM signal layer (Phase 2+).

# ── Recommended: DeepSeek (cheapest, ~$0.14/million tokens) ──────────────────
# Sign up at: platform.deepseek.com
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...

# ── Alternative: OpenRouter (access to many models, pay-per-use) ─────────────
# Sign up at: openrouter.ai
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...

# ── Alternative: Anthropic Claude (you may already have this) ────────────────
# Sign up at: console.anthropic.com
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Free option: Ollama (local, no API cost, needs ~8GB RAM) ─────────────────
# Install from: ollama.ai
# Then run: ollama pull qwen2.5:7b
# No key needed — Ollama runs locally.
# Note: Your RTX 3050 (4GB VRAM) can run 7B models in GPU mode.
